atg.commerce.order.abandoned
Class ReanimateAbandonedOrder

java.lang.Object
  atg.process.action.ActionImpl
      atg.commerce.order.abandoned.ReanimateAbandonedOrder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Action
public class ReanimateAbandonedOrder
extends ActionImpl

This action checks to see if the current order is abandoned. If so, it changes the abandonmentState to "REANIMATED" and fires an OrderReanimated event if configured to do so. This is done by calling the reanimateAbandonedOrder method of AbandonedOrderTools
